1. For running the python scripts, I have used python2.7.

2. The command line for running the scripts is
   python2.7 script.py --image  directory/image

3. For running the detector_flare.py, the image file small.jpg
as test image required for the template macth algorithm.

4. The required packages are OPEN CV3, numpy, argparse and imutils.

pip install imutils
